# Imports e Estrutura de Diretórios

## Use Statements Pattern

### Para Controllers
```php
use App\Http\Controllers\Controller;
use App\Facades\Google\{
    GoogleProjectService,
    GoogleProjectCreateService,
    GoogleProjectUpdateService,
    GoogleProjectFilterService
};
use App\Facades\Repositories\Project\{
    CampaignFilterValueRepository,
    AccountRepository
};
use Illuminate\Http\{JsonResponse, Response};
```

### Para Services
```php
use App\Contracts\Services\Google\[ServiceName]Interface;
use App\Exceptions\{ClientException, UnauthorizedException};
use App\Facades\Google\Client\ClientService;
use App\Facades\Logging\ApiLog;
use App\Facades\Repositories\Project\{
    AccountRepository,
    ProductRepository
};
use App\Traits\Google\GoogleProjectCampaignUtils;
use Exception;
```

## Ordem de Imports

1. PHP nativo/vendor packages
2. `App\Contracts` (Interfaces)
3. `App\Entities`
4. `App\Enums`
5. `App\Exceptions`
6. `App\Facades` (agrupadas por domínio)
7. `App\Http\Controllers\Controller`
8. `App\Traits`
9. `Illuminate` classes (agrupadas com `{}`)
10. Vendor packages (Google, etc.)

## Agrupamento com `{}`

```php
// ✅ CORRETO - Agrupar classes do mesmo namespace
use App\Facades\Google\{
    GoogleProjectService,
    GoogleProjectCreateService,
    GoogleProjectUpdateService
};

// ❌ ERRADO - Imports separados
use App\Facades\Google\GoogleProjectService;
use App\Facades\Google\GoogleProjectCreateService;
use App\Facades\Google\GoogleProjectUpdateService;
```

## 🚫 Proibição de Imports Inline

**NUNCA use imports inline (fully qualified class name no código). SEMPRE declare no bloco de `use` statements.**

```php
// ❌ ERRADO - Import inline (fully qualified)
public function getAccount(): array
{
    $exception = new \App\Exceptions\ClientException('Erro');
    $log = \App\Facades\Logging\ApiLog::info('...');
    throw new \Exception('Erro genérico');
}

// ✅ CORRETO - Import declarado no topo do arquivo
use App\Exceptions\ClientException;
use App\Facades\Logging\ApiLog;
use Exception;

public function getAccount(): array
{
    $exception = new ClientException('Erro');
    $log = ApiLog::info('...');
    throw new Exception('Erro genérico');
}
```

### Motivos
1. **Legibilidade**: Fácil identificar todas as dependências no topo do arquivo
2. **Consistência**: Padrão único em todo o projeto
3. **Manutenibilidade**: Alterações de namespace afetam apenas o bloco de imports
4. **Code Review**: Revisão rápida das dependências utilizadas

## Estrutura de Diretórios

```
app/
├── Http/Controllers/[Domain]/
├── Services/[Domain]/
├── Contracts/
│   ├── Services/[Domain]/
│   └── Repositories/[Domain]/
├── Facades/
│   ├── [Domain]/
│   └── Repositories/[Domain]/
├── Repositories/[Domain]/
├── Entities/[Domain]/
├── Enums/[Domain]/
└── Exceptions/
```

## Naming Conventions

| Tipo | Convenção | Exemplo |
|------|-----------|---------|
| Controllers | `[Domain]Controller` | `GoogleProjectController`, `ProductCenterController` |
| Services | `[Name]Service` | `GoogleProjectService`, `PartnerPersistenceService` |
| Interfaces | `[ServiceName]Interface` | `GoogleProjectServiceInterface` |
| Facades | Mesmo nome do Service | `GoogleProjectService` (em `App\Facades`) |
| Repositories | `[Name]Repository` | `ProductRepository`, `AccountRepository` |
| Entities | `[Name]Entity` | `CampaignEntity`, `AccountEntity` |
| Enums | `[Name]Enum` | `CampaignStatusEnum`, `ErrorMessageEnum` |

## Domínios Principais

### Google Domain
- **Ads**: GoogleAdsService, BudgetRecommendationService
- **ProductCenter**: ProductCenterProductService, ProductCenterWebsiteService
- **Client**: ClientService, ExternalClientService
- **Core**: GoogleProjectService, GoogleProjectCreateService, GoogleProjectUpdateService

### Project Domain
- **Account**: AccountRepository, AccountCampaignRepository
- **Product**: ProductRepository
- **Campaign**: CampaignFilterRepository, CampaignFilterValueRepository
- **Shop**: ShopRepository

### Store Domain
- **Product**: ProductRepository (API)
- **Order**: OrderRepository (API)
- **Customer**: CustomerRepository (API)
- **Category**: CategoryRepository (API)
- **Brand**: BrandRepository (API)

### Core Domain
- **Account**: AccountDetailsService
- **Partner**: PartnerPersistenceService

## Aplicação por Domínio

```php
// Interface → Facade → Implementation
App\Contracts\Services\[Domain]\[Service]Interface
App\Facades\[Domain]\[Service]
App\Services\[Domain]\[Service]

// Repository: DbRepository (banco) | ApiRepository (APIs)
App\Repositories\[Domain]\[Repository] extends DbRepository
App\Repositories\Store\[Repository] extends ApiRepository
```
